{"tid":2505841,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣東話研究】唔使5分鐘，問下你粵語使用習慣","createTime":"2021-04-27T02:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T18:56:50.000Z","uid":138409,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f454053d6722eb07596c8b8cc72f50131d974c","tid":2505841,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個問卷真係好簡單㗎咋<br />\n如果你覺得5p字「吾系甘牙」好煩<br />\n噉就更加要做呢個問卷，表達你嘅意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n研究計劃：Data-Driven Analysis of Orthographic Variations in Hong Kong Written Cantonese &lt;Ref. no. 2019-2020-0465&gt;<br />\n研究目的：了解香港粵語使用者喺書寫粵語時嘅習慣。歡迎以香港粵語為母語嘅人士參加。<br />\n負責人：劉擇明博士負責監督並執行<br />\n<br />\n- 研究方法 -<br />\n本研究採用問卷形式進行。問卷分為兩部份<br />\n第一部份有 25 組粵語詞組或短句，請<span class=\"gold\">揀出你使用唔同寫法嘅傾向</span>；<br />\n第二部分有 6 題，主要關於你嘅背景同<span class=\"gold\">對書寫粵語嘅睇法</span>。全卷均為選擇題，<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">5 分鐘內可以完成。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n- 風險 -<br />\n你嘅參與純屬自願性質，參與本研究冇任何已知風險。你有權隨時決定退出呢項研究，唔會因此引致任何不良後果。凡有關你嘅個人資料將會保密，一切資料嘅編碼只有研究人員得悉。<br />\n<br />\n- 研究結果嘅發佈 -<br />\n本次研究嘅成果將會喺學術會議或期刊發佈，收集到嘅數據亦會整合並用於自然語言處理的程式開發。<br />\n<br />\n如想獲得更多有關本項研究嘅資料，請聯絡劉擇明博士。（電郵：lchaakming@eduhk.hk；電話：2948 7280）<br />\n<br />\n如對本研究嘅操守有任何意見，可隨時聯絡香港教育大學人類實驗對象操守委員會。（電郵：hrec@eduhk.hk；地址：新界大埔露屏路10號香港教育大學研究與發展事務處）"},{"pid":"06fee9ead7d6123f193319e0b2150664adff0075","tid":2505841,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a3b28ea5d9e0f7fc668d08baa5d99d3e9a26542d","tid":2505841,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:26:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d5c23a8474fbf74cf9e0710bc33d15ca01bad4dc","tid":2505841,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:27:12.000Z","msg":"做完呢分問卷<br />\n可以過呢邊玩添<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【詞彙聯想】5分鐘玩個遊戲，就可以幫廣東話研究出一分力<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2250282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2250282</a>"},{"pid":"ea9b64faf57292ed41343edcfa2aba21e45695dc","tid":2505841,"uid":9116,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"問卷條Link呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392c742d0931f08110d8a132e8f27752b7934563","tid":2505841,"uid":138409,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ea9b64faf57292ed41343edcfa2aba21e45695dc","tid":2505841,"uid":9116,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"問卷條Link呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:28:16.000Z","msg":"屌柒咗 sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSePIvhwHDs4F4Tt-kexbuHBDhqCypQw_Vm3SIJpGm8iEH4Xag/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSePIvhwHDs4F4Tt-kexbuHBDhqCypQw_Vm3SIJpGm8iEH4Xag%2Fviewform&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B61Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=3a866f27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSePIvhwHDs4F4Tt-kexbuHBDhqCypQw_Vm3SIJpGm8iEH4Xag/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"d683138d61f27134895e2b33c351abba9280e213","tid":2505841,"uid":14623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9f08c16956b261aa42e66c4ca2fd561c7ed886ea","tid":2505841,"uid":394651,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"問卷就我做，credit就你攞"},{"pid":"0932c9e7d19a249533f5dc6e68b2b0ff0ae09968","tid":2505841,"uid":305674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T03:06:31.0